I had good success with this after changing PIN_A1 to PIN_A4 in the code. Initially I made a mistake in my PCB layout based on the schematic for pin 3 signal out.  PIN_A4 corresponds to the pin shown in the schematic.

I see super good efficiency running .6 amps from 15v across the primary with a 5/8&quot; arc.  I&#039;m very impressed by how well this works with a N channel irf840 mosfet, sony color tv flyback xformer and delay_us (28) ; 

Great design.
